### Research Questions & Hypotheses  
- **What menu items are the most popular?**  
  - ğŸŸ© *Hypothesis:* Items with higher sales and customer ratings are the most popular.  

- **What factors influence menu item demand?**  
  - ğŸŸ© *Hypothesis:* Positive reviews, competitive pricing, and frequent promotions increase demand.  

- **Which cuisines are most preferred by customers?**  
  - ğŸŸ© *Hypothesis:* Cuisines with frequent orders and high customer ratings are preferred.  

- **How does pricing impact menu item popularity?**  
  - ğŸŸ© *Hypothesis:* Items with optimal pricing (balancing affordability and value) attract more orders.  

